divs: Sighting DetailsBriefly, three events: 1. 1958 - Walker AFB, Roswell N. Mex. - black lines moving across the sky from west to east at sundown. (one other witness) 2. 1996 - Joseph, Oregon - something white and round oscillating over lake Wallowa and then stabilizing before shooting over head to disappear into the clouds (no other witnesses). 3. 2000 - Thousand Oaks, CA - several (8-10) luminous objects in a random pattern moving across the sky. One seen to repeatedly dart from "formation" and then return (several potential witnesses). For the record: I am a well educated individual with flight experience and a solid knowledge of aircraft.
Summary: group of 8-10 luminous objects - one darting from formation
trends: There have been 17 other sightings in Thousand Oaks
There were no other sightings in Thousand Oaks on or around November 30th 1999
